496
00:25:47,670 --> 00:25:50,880
"El Comando de Defensa
Aeroespacial Americano, NORAD,

497
00:25:50,880 --> 00:25:53,220
realizó simulacros de intercepción,

498
00:25:54,390 --> 00:25:57,760
simulando aviones secuestrados
